        <item>
            <title>開篷電動跑車 MG Cyberster 右軚版到港，兩個版本一換一 52.9 萬起</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/25/mg-cyberster-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mg-cyberster-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/25/mg-cyberster-2/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 09:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MG Cyberster]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1258506</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>MG Cyberster 電動開篷跑車右軚版本正式在香港亮相，這款新車早前已以左軚版本在香港展出過，昨日終於迎來右軚版抵港。香港代理商亦公佈了這款新車的「一換一」售價，77kWh 單馬達 2WD 後驅版「一換一」車價為 HK$529,000 起，而頂級 77kWh 雙馬達 4WD 版「一換一」售價則為 HK$589,000 起。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258516" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1513-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1513-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1513.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258517" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1512-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1512-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1512.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>MG Cyberster 這款電動跑車以新穎設計和高效能為賣點，配備了可收放軟篷設計，滿足駕駛愛好者對跑車的追求，並帶來電動車獨特駕駛體驗。Cyberster 擁有優雅而前衞的外觀設計，加上高科技內裝配置，成為市場上競爭力十足的選擇。這款車的底盤由 Marco Fainello 設計，他曾參與 Ferrari F1 一級方程式賽車及 488 GTB 等車型的研發。該車型採用前雙搖臂及後五連桿懸掛設定，讓車輛在高速行駛時依然保持穩定操控。</p><p>香港版 Cyberster 有兩選選擇，其中 MG Cyberster 四驅 77kWh 雙馬達 4WD 版本，搭載前後馬達，能提供 503 ps 馬力及 725 Nm 扭力，0-100 km/h 加速僅需 3.2 秒。該車款配備由寧德時代提供的 77 kWh 電池，電池厚度僅 110 mm，根據 WLTP 標準測試，續航距離達 443 公里。</p><p>Cyberster 配備了標誌性剪刀式車門，這款車門提供極具辨識度的外觀，還內置雷達探測功能，能夠檢測車門頂部及車側是否存在障礙物。車內設計同樣注重細節，包括符合人體工學設計的跑車桶椅、中控台上的 7 吋屏幕。一體化數碼儀錶由左右兩組 7 吋屏幕及中央 10.25 吋屏幕組成。中控台搭載自家 OS 系統，應用了速度高的 Snapdragon 8155 晶片及 Unreal Engine，確保操作流暢。車內還配置了 BOSE 音響系統，軟篷頂可透過一鍵式按鈕操作，能在 10 秒內完成開合，即使在車速達 50 km/h 時亦能順利操作。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258512" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1509-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1509-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1509.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258507" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1516-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1516-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1516.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258508" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1511-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1511-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1511.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258509" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1515-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1515-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1515.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258510" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1505-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1505-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1505.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258511" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1502-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1502-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1502.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>MG Cyberster 4WD 雙馬達版</p><p>傳動：77kWh 鋰電+前後馬達，四驅</p><p>馬力/扭力：544ps/725Nm</p><p>0 至 100km/h：3.2 秒</p><p>續航力：444km(WLTP)</p><p>尺碼：4,533 x 1,912 x 1,328mm</p><p>售價：HK$589,000 起（一換一）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258513" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_-694x324.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="324" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_-694x324.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_-1-694x324.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="324" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_-1-694x324.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/25/mg-cyberster-2/life-tech/auto/">開篷電動跑車 MG Cyberster 右軚版到港，兩個版本一換一 52.9 萬起</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
